about.title: About
about.content: Healthcare Compared was built to be a simple way of comparing insurance plans each year. To get started, click on the hamburger icon then click plans.

disclaimer.title: Disclaimer
disclaimer.content: "Healthcare Compared" is a tool created to facilitate healthcare plan comparisons and provide estimates based on the data you input. The information presented on this web application is for informational and educational purposes only and should not be considered as professional financial or healthcare advice.
